headline: Rodents on the run: Orkin Canada releases 2025 list of Rattiest Cities
summary: Orkin Canada’s annual national “Rattiest Cities” list is out!MISSISSAUGA, Ontario, Dec. 09, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Orkin Canada has released its annual list of the top 25 “rattiest” cities in Canada, with Toronto once again claiming the top spot. This year's list saw Toronto and Victoria battle it out for first place in the rat race, and welcomed Moncton and Ottawa back into the top 10.
